text: Felix Teodor Hamrin, born 14 January 1875, dead 27 November 1937, was a Swedish politician. He was the leader of the liberal Freeminded People's Party. He also served as Prime Minister of Sweden from 6 August to 24 September 1932. == References == Category:1875 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Government ministers of Sweden Category:Prime ministers of Sweden
